#                             .: .bashrc - 2011-03-26 18:46 :.
#
#                  My .bashrc, aliases, bash functions, colors are put in
#              serperate file in ~/.bash/ trying to make some order in caos.
#
#           .: Andreas Persson (greyscale, greu) andreas(at)greyscale(dot)se :.
